<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Dashboard</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <style>
    .dashboard-container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .welcome-box {
      background-color: #f0f8ff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-left: 5px solid #4CAF50;
    }
    nav ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 10px;
    }
    nav li a {
      display: block;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      color: #333;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    nav li a:hover {
      background-color: #ddd;
    }
    .logout-btn {
      background-color: #f44336 !important;
      color: white !important;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="dashboard-container">
    <div class="welcome-box">
      <h1>Bem-vindo, <%= user.username %>!</h1>
      <p>Você está logado com sucesso usando a autenticação baseada em SQLite.</p>
    </div>

    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/vulnerable">Módulo Vulnerável (XSS)</a></li>
        <li><a href="/secure">Módulo Seguro (XSS Sanitizado)</a></li>
        <li><a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">Sair</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
